text: Patrick Gudauskas (born November 20, 1985 in La Jolla) is an American/Lithuanian professional surfer. He won several surfing competitions including the 2008 O'Neill Sebastian Inlet Pro. ==References== ==External links== * Profile at World Surf League Category:1985 births Category:Living people Category:Sportspeople from San Diego Category:American surfers Category:Lithuanian surfers Lithuanian Decent
